## API Endpoints
### Health
- `GET /api/health`
- `GET /api/health/version`

### Employees
- `GET /api/employees`
- `GET /api/employees/{id}`
- `GET /api/employees/department/{dept}`
- `POST /api/employees`
- `PUT /api/employees/{id}`
- `DELETE /api/employees/{id}`

### Oracle Database
- `GET /api/oracle/test-connection`
- `GET /api/oracle/version`
- `GET /api/oracle/tables`
- `POST /api/oracle/execute-query`

### Schema Management
- `POST /api/schema/tables/clone`
- `GET /api/schema/tables/{name}/ddl`
- `DELETE /api/schema/tables/{name}`
